parameters:
Would you like to view the event? It's for the quota's
outside rounds.

\nc<Saki>(Is senpai on a business trip, I wonder? I'd like to gather
a bit more energy in preparation for the accounting...)

\nc<Saki>Ah, isn't this that sex app from before? I hadn't deleted it
yet...

\nc<Saki>It seems to have a fair number of users... though most of
them are men.

\nc<Saki>That event was pretty tough, but I did gather a lot of
energy...

\nc<Saki>Other succubi seem to use it quite a bit too, right? Despite
how much they disliked it at the event venue, there are so
many familiar faces...
\nc<Saki>Maybe I'll try it just one more time...?
